Tyler Perry Studios celebrated its grand opening with the creme de la creme of Hollywood at a star-studded gala. The 330-acre filming complex at the former home of Fort McPherson officially opened its doors Saturday, October 5, as the only major film studio in the nation owned by an African-American. Major Hollywood stars including  Jermaine Dupri, Usher, Ludacris, Bernice King, John Lewis and Stacey Abrams major Hollywood stars including Halle Berry, Cecily Tyson, Whoopie Goldberg, Oprah Winfrey, Samuel Jackson, Spike Lee and Viola Davis just to name a few, graced the red event in support of Tyler Perry. See all lovely photos below. *** Ladies First ATLANTA, GEORGIA – OCTOBER 05: Tina Knowles attends Tyler Perry Studios grand opening gala at Tyler Perry Studios on October 05, 2019 in Atlanta, Georgia. (Photo by Paras Griffin/Getty Images for Tyler Perry Studios) ATLANTA, GEORGIA – OCTOBER 05: Taraji P. Henson attends Tyler Perry Studios grand opening gala at Tyler Perry Studios on October 05, 2019 in Atlanta, Georgia. (Photo by Paras Griffin/Getty Images for Tyler Perry Studios) ATLANTA, GEORGIA – OCTOBER 05: Kelly Rowland attends Tyler Perry Studios grand opening gala at Tyler Perry Studios on October 05, 2019 in Atlanta, Georgia. (Photo by Paras Griffin/Getty Images for Tyler Perry Studios) ATLANTA, GEORGIA – OCTOBER 05: Michelle Williams attends Tyler Perry Studios grand opening gala at Tyler Perry Studios on October 05, 2019 in Atlanta, Georgia. (Photo by Paras Griffin/Getty Images for Tyler Perry Studios) ATLANTA, GEORGIA – OCTOBER 05: Jenifer Lewis attends Tyler Perry Studios grand opening gala at Tyler Perry Studios on October 05, 2019 in Atlanta, Georgia. (Photo by Paras Griffin/Getty Images for Tyler Perry Studios) ATLANTA, GEORGIA – OCTOBER 05: Monica attends Tyler Perry Studios grand opening gala at Tyler Perry Studios on October 05, 2019 in Atlanta, Georgia. (Photo by Paras Griffin/Getty Images for Tyler Perry Studios) ATLANTA, GEORGIA – OCTOBER 05: Pat